Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today I think I'll tell you a story about a certain Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Persona Black Frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he lived alone for over thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While enduring the solitude, he prayed to the sky, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleading, "Give me a friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the god he served granted him one for a single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the two of them frolicked through the fields, as happy as could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the sun set, his friend vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Frost regretted his request,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for he never would've asked for a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he had known he would've been left sad and lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence Black Flo—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Flau—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mispronounce it.
