Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abaddon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out{senpai}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lightning attack's coming up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks won't connect with her zooming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to slow her down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, you're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, you're cool even when you're old!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, you still up and kickin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashter, I shink I'm forgetting shomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hurting these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I can't fill their bodies with holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was inept at making friends ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after my parents died in an accident and my grandfather took me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never made any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather would secretly let me help with his client's cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, people started calling me Junior Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, I should fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I fuse them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we didn't have to get old!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, everyone went nuts over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my status as a "child" was sufficient to offend many of those whom I worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With time, I can become an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about being a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll never change, even after I grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to give you a new life as my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suck at making friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big fuckin' deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crude simpletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could be young again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remem-beared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bear-come young again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you have remembered that sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to make your elders wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get our youth back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Energy Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Re-energize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so full of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one huge fly!
