Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saw everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like being a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you always dress like a boy?{Or maybe naoto x shinji ikari crossover fanfic}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sex doesn't fit my ideal image of a detective.{Fuck, I ship everyone with shinji}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had the slightest "concrete" reason to look down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one would need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that!{NO! THE GLASS CEILING IS REAL!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that what you yearn for isn't to become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or to become a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try facing yourself.{OMG THAT'S THE SONG NAME!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept ignoring you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pretending you didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been inside me.{awww yeaaa}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am you...{made weirder by the fact she keeps saying "boku"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are me.{do any girls in japan actually use boku?}{she's trying to be a dude, faggot. and azusa does in the amagmi ss op}{I hear it a lot in songs, but i'm talking about conversation, bro.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dream to become a cool, hard-boiled detective someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I should yearn for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what I must strive for isn't to become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to accept myself for who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a devious bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you kept something like this hidden for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder the perpetrator has eluded the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
