Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, she really put her life on the line for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never doubted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd all come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no genius at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too damn reckless!{he wants to fuck you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we know.{because he's gay for you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case isn't over yet.{but he justifies his gayness since you're actually a girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you've proven that to us.{so... episode end? episode end.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, welcome ba—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard? They found Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, the Detective Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We attend the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went missing for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, they just found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to put a scare into everyone... Yeesh!{>everone... reminds me of this troll someone on rizon tried on gaia http://www.gaiaonline.com/forum/welcome-to-gaia/hai-ever1-im-new-xddddd-p/t.70641627/ didn't exactly work as a troll}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't already know that he'd been found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really oughtta do somethin' about that habit of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors spread fast out here, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he got sulky after being given the boot and ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was taken off the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I tell you, I was shocked to hear that he up and vanished like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there had been a fourth kidnapping and murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't have any concrete evidence with that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we gonna make a case like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Dojima's instinct is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe there really is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I gotta say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit running your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go study like a normal student...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I killed the mood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I can totally understand why Dojima's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the case to us police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would suck if you got caught up in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are more scary things going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing scary's gonna happen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not, I got the most brains in the whole police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, was that too hard to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "got brains" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means he's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So things'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
