Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}Thank you for the other day.{She was actually thanking him for the sex}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}But what's with that uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}After some thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}I decided to stick with what I've been wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, it's the Detective Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's no prince! He's a she!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}I'm kinda shocked, but also a little disappointed.{girls in background}{i can barely hear this line at all, could easily be nuked imo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If that's a girl, then holy cow!{overlaps with previous}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}Goodness, rumors sure spread quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,716)}Just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was hoping I could discuss the case with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. We did leave things hanging since the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:15:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone lurking in this town is behind all of these kidnappings and murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(m 439 643 l 484 670 531 689 598 704 653 705 690 703 747 691 792 672 835 649 863 626)}Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(m 526 646 l 561 657 590 664 619 667 650 668 671 667 697 665 751 648 798 625)}Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My old lady couldn't make this if she tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vichyssoise you made just recently was amazing, too.{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vichyssoise}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want more! But I don't want to finish it all.{overlaps with previous}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, listen to what Naoto has to say!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were at home when you got kidnapped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started when my doorbell rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I opened the front door, I saw no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as alarm bells sounded in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone grabbed me roughly from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and covered my mouth with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately afterward,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was put into something like a sack and carried on someone's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how could you remember all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was psychologically prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too damn calm about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by their actions and body type, I'd say the culprit is definitely a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard no conversations or voices,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I believe he is acting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a single impact,{my dick is now diamonds}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I assume is when I was thrown inside the TV, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the time from kidnapping to that point seemed too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how long did this take?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he caught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was over in a few minutes.{surprised jukey didn't comment on this line tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he threw you in the TV right after catching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no question that the culprit is the same in each case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about that Kubo guy who killed Mr. Morooka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a copycat killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the question remains, though, as to how he learned of the world inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's what was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo could enter the TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't he kill King Moron the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he didn't understand the other world as well as the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can now enter it myself, it wouldn't occur to me to use it for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kubo's criminal act did verify one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer isn't retrieving the bodies and hanging them upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is simply what happens to the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when someone is killed over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he isn't trying to send some crazy message, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could ask Kubo in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,much of our speculation could be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, if you were so calm, couldn't you have, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean you needed to catch him, but you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!{KYUN}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She {\i1}is{\i0} a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, r-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to you talk, that totally slipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got balls for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What makes you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this case is no longer just a job or someone else's affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to join your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be reassuring if a famous detective teamed up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy now, Kanji?{nihihi~}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And ta-da! Here are your glasses, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, I can sympathize with your drive to find yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to help you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're a sweetie pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I flirt with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cooperate with you on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my, my, my, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have a suggestion regarding Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you spend tomorrow after school with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a doctor to take a look at Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I thought having a doctor take a look at him might be a good first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that fog on the other side, not to mention our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should make sure that it isn't negatively affecting our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's results appear normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Teddie? Did you find out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned that we don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had them take an X-ray, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even had them retake it several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it wise to take that without getting permission first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I intend to return it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the results to your physical exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too em-bear-rassing if I'm the only one who gets fully exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for some thrilling announcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, if you wanna announce something, start with the girls' three sizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Are you a total moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, is this accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't measure you incorrectly, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Which way should I interpret that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool it, perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the doctors were unable to find any physical problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we will no longer be needing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let me take a peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}N-No! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Hanamura! No peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait. Were those sizes legit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto's bust size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But dang, she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women fight to be their own selves, even if their secrets get exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough.{TRUE DAT}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching Naoto has taught me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy for me to act tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we went to save Naoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I saw her accept herself and strive to be true to herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've decided to be myself and help others understand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're wondering why I shared this with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's because you saved my life, and you're my best bud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue being friends.
