Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even put down her grade and class number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going by the heart seal on the envelope, I doubt this is a commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's no reason to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am only interested in commissions for more cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is something I would like your help with after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's our rainy day special.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has been able to discern everything that goes in the Mega Beef Bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always manage to throw me off somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:42.92,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}I look at the rustic scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:45.63,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}along the path to school
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the case
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:51.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}we walked together {kimi to aruita tsuugakuro hinabiru keshiki mitsumete}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is a series of big events.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:56.89,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}Campus in spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath the meat is... more meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:23:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more meat and more meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:00.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}the summer festival {haru no koutei kasenshiki natsu matsuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this based on some sort of set law?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:04.52,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}These were the days we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.53,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}shoulder-to-shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Detective Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:12.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(150,150)}laughing together {minna de waratte katayose sugoshiteta hibi}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:19.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From past to present {kono ninake nai nichijou wo nagamete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:26.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}looked back on these
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:29.51,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}carefree days {kako kara ima made sugoshite kita yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:37.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}From today to tomorrow {kyou kara asu ashita kara mirai he}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:49.86,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\t(\b0\c&H303030&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}We move forward while treasuring the bonds we've made {minna to kizuita kizuna himete aruki dasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.62,screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,522)\fnLCD Solid\fs66\c&H2E312E&\blur0.5}STOP HELPING PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hit-and-run near Samegawa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just can't get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to keep out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're running away from her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd go to Heaven if I died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect her!
